        "created_at": "2020-03-09T14:41:10.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Agree on your note, but I love the 2006 Geynale even more, I have to say. From my cellar, the Geynale is beginning to enter the zone and is a lot less monolithic than it was six or seven years ago. I still have the better part of two cases I think.</p>",
