        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/j/ba9def/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2022-10-30T03:00:18.698Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I had the 2006 Geynale last night and man was it singing! You were right\u2026 way better than it\u2019s little<br>\nBrother.</p>\n<p>These seem to just be coming into the sweet spot of development for me. Starting to show secondary flavors while not losing original core of fruit.</p>\n<p>Has anyone else opened one recently?</p>",
